The paper presents a method for liver tumor segmentation using convolutional neural networks and random forest classifiers. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of neural networks and machine learning algorithms for medical image analysis makes it relevant to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also deals with medical imaging and segmentation, which could fall under the medical imaging (cs.MED) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
